  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Fix Embedded Gallery Overlay Display Issue in Single News View\n\nResolve rendering problems with the embedded gallery overlay component when displayed within individual news article pages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify the specific visual/functional issues with the gallery overlay (e.g., positioning, z-index, dimensions, visibility)\n- Locate the gallery overlay component implementation in single news view templates\n- Check for CSS conflicts or missing styles affecting the overlay\n- Verify overlay behavior across different viewport sizes (mobile, tablet, desktop)\n- Ensure gallery images load and display correctly within the overlay\n- Test overlay interaction controls (close button, navigation arrows, thumbnails)\n- Verify overlay works with various gallery sizes (single image, multiple images)\n- Confirm overlay properly overlays content without breaking page layout\n- Test in major browsers for cross-browser compatibility\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- News articles with no images or single image\n- Gallery with very large or very small images\n- Overlay behavior when triggered multiple times rapidly\n- Keyboard navigation and accessibility (ESC to close, arrow keys for navigation)",
